responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "2C5E977A447874591E2D6EB2EB2AEA82", "I am less interested in what each foul token is than what the cult seeks to do with them. I know not of essence-work, the Streamweavers ken that weave. My worth is in blade and bone. What I wrest from the Sighted I give to the \'Weavers, and from those trophies they cull the charged dust with which we consecrate our camps.")
